The paper deals with image denoising, inpainting, deconvolution, and reconstruction, which are all related to computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). The use of hierarchical dependencies across multiple scales suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper also mentions the use of Bayesian inference, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
